{"id":791,"parent_id":769,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":791,"title":"Jeremiah 22","subtitle":"","short_title":"Jer.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 22"],[".studySummary",["i","David’s throne stands or falls according to the obedience of the kings—The judgments of the Lord rest upon the kings of Judah."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.1","order":"02.25.022.52273"},["b","1"],"Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; Go down to the house of the king of Judah, and speak there this word,"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.2","order":"02.25.022.52274"},["b","2"],"And say, Hear the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", O king of Judah, that sittest upon the throne of David, thou, and thy servants, and thy people that enter in by these gates:"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.3","order":"02.25.022.52275"},["b","3"],"Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; Execute ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"judgment"],"and righteousness, and deliver the spoiled out of the hand of the oppressor: and do no wrong, do no violence to the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"stranger"],", the fatherless, nor the widow, neither shed innocent",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"blood"],"in this place."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.4","order":"02.25.022.52276"},["b","4"],"For if ye do this thing indeed, then shall there enter in by the gates of this house",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"kings"],"sitting upon the throne of David, riding in chariots and on horses, he, and his servants, and his people."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.5","order":"02.25.022.52277"},["b","5"],"But if ye will not hear these words, I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"swear"],"by myself, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", that this house shall become a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"desolation"],"."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.6","order":"02.25.022.52278"},["b","6"],"For thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"unto the king’s house of Judah; Thou",["i","art"],"Gilead unto me,",["i","and"],"the head of Lebanon:",["i","yet"],"surely I will make thee a wilderness,",["i","and"],"cities",["i","which"],"are not inhabited."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.7","order":"02.25.022.52279"},["b","7"],"And I will prepare destroyers against thee, every one with his weapons: and they shall cut down thy choice",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"cedars"],", and cast",["i","them"],"into the fire."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.8","order":"02.25.022.52280"},["b","8"],"And many nations shall pass by this city, and they shall say every man to his neighbour, Wherefore hath the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"done"],"thus unto this great city?"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.9","order":"02.25.022.52281"},["b","9"],"Then they shall answer, Because they have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"forsaken"],"the covenant of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"their God, and worshipped other gods, and served them."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.10","order":"02.25.022.52282"},["b","10"],"¶Weep ye not for the dead, neither bemoan him:",["i","but"],"weep sore for him that goeth away: for he shall return no more, nor see his native country."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.11","order":"02.25.022.52283"},["b","11"],"For thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"touching",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"Shallum"],"the son of Josiah king of Judah, which reigned instead of Josiah his father, which went forth out of this place; He shall not return thither any more:"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.12","order":"02.25.022.52284"},["b","12"],"But he shall die in the place whither they have led him captive, and shall see this land no more."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.13","order":"02.25.022.52285"},["b","13"],"¶",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"Woe"],"unto him that buildeth his house by",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"unrighteousness"],", and his chambers by wrong;",["i","that"],"useth his neighbour’s service without",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_13c"},"wages"],", and giveth him not for his work;"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.14","order":"02.25.022.52286"},["b","14"],"That saith, I will build me a wide house and large chambers, and cutteth him out windows; and",["i","it is"],"ceiled with cedar, and painted with vermilion."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.15","order":"02.25.022.52287"},["b","15"],"Shalt thou reign, because thou closest",["i","thyself"],"in cedar? did not thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"father"],"eat and drink, and do judgment and justice,",["i","and"],"then",["i","it was"],"well with him?"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.16","order":"02.25.022.52288"},["b","16"],"He judged the cause of the poor and needy; then",["i","it was"],"well",["i","with him: was"],"not this to know me? saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.17","order":"02.25.022.52289"},["b","17"],"But thine eyes and thine heart",["i","are"],"not but for thy covetousness, and for to shed innocent blood, and for oppression, and for violence, to do",["i","it."]],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.18","order":"02.25.022.52290"},["b","18"],"Therefore thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"concerning Jehoiakim the son of Josiah king of Judah; They shall not lament for him,",["i","saying,"],"Ah my brother! or, Ah sister! they shall not lament for him,",["i","saying,"],"Ah lord! or, Ah his glory!"],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.19","order":"02.25.022.52291"},["b","19"],"He shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"buried"],"with the burial of an ass, drawn and cast forth beyond the gates of Jerusalem."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.20","order":"02.25.022.52292"},["b","20"],"¶Go up to Lebanon, and cry; and lift up thy voice in Bashan, and cry from the passages: for all thy lovers are destroyed."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.21","order":"02.25.022.52293"},["b","21"],"I spake unto thee in thy prosperity;",["i","but"],"thou saidst, I will not hear. This",["i","hath been"],"thy manner from thy youth, that thou",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"obeyedst not"],"my voice."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.22","order":"02.25.022.52294"},["b","22"],"The wind shall eat up all thy pastors, and thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"lovers"],"shall go into captivity: surely then shalt thou be ashamed and confounded for all thy wickedness."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.23","order":"02.25.022.52295"},["b","23"],"O inhabitant of Lebanon, that makest thy nest in the cedars, how",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"gracious"],"shalt thou be when pangs come upon thee, the pain as of a woman in travail!"],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.24","order":"02.25.022.52296"},["b","24"],["i","As"],"I live, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", though",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"Coniah"],"the son of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"Jehoiakim"],"king of Judah were the signet upon my right hand, yet would I pluck thee thence;"],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.25","order":"02.25.022.52297"},["b","25"],"And I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"give"],"thee into the hand of them that seek thy life, and into the hand",["i","of them"],"whose face thou fearest, even into the hand of Nebuchadrezzar king of Babylon, and into the hand of the Chaldeans."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.26","order":"02.25.022.52298"},["b","26"],"And I will cast thee out, and thy mother that bare thee, into another country, where ye were not born; and there shall ye die."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.27","order":"02.25.022.52299"},["b","27"],"But to the land whereunto they desire to return, thither shall they not return."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.28","order":"02.25.022.52300"},["b","28"],["i","Is"],"this man Coniah a despised broken idol?",["i","is he"],"a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"vessel"],"wherein",["i","is"],"no pleasure? wherefore are they cast out, he and his seed, and are cast into a land which they know not?"],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.29","order":"02.25.022.52301"},["b","29"],"O earth, earth, earth, hear the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"word"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.30","order":"02.25.022.52302"},["b","30"],"Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],",",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_30a"},"Write"],"ye this man childless, a man",["i","that"],"shall not prosper in his days: for no man of his seed shall prosper, sitting upon the throne of David, and ruling any more in Judah."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.3a","order":"02.25.022.52303"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/justice"},"TG Justice"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.3b","order":"02.25.022.52305"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/7.6"},"Jer. 7:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.3c","order":"02.25.022.52307"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/132.19"},"D&C 132:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.4a","order":"02.25.022.52309"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/17.25"},"Jer. 17:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.5a","order":"02.25.022.52311"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/6.8"},"Amos 6:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.5b","order":"02.25.022.52313"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.25"},"Ps. 69:25"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/12.7"},"Jer. 12:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/23.38"},"Matt. 23:38"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/13.35"},"Luke 13:35"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.7a","order":"02.25.022.52315"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/37.24"},"Isa. 37:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.8a","order":"02.25.022.52317"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/9.8"},"1 Kgs. 9:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.9a","order":"02.25.022.52319"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/29.25"},"Deut. 29:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.11a","order":"02.25.022.52321"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/3.15"},"1 Chr. 3:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.13a","order":"02.25.022.52323"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/james/5.4.1-6"},"James 5:4 (1–6)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.13b","order":"02.25.022.52325"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/23.37"},"2 Kgs. 23:37"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/19.6"},"Ezek. 19:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"13c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.13c","order":"02.25.022.52327"},["b","13c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/wages"},"TG Wages"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.15a","order":"02.25.022.52329"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/23.25"},"2 Kgs. 23:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.19a","order":"02.25.022.52331"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/6.3"},"Eccl. 6:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.21a","order":"02.25.022.52333"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/disobedience"},"TG Disobedience"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.22a","order":"02.25.022.52335"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.2"},"Lam. 1:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.23a","order":"02.25.022.52337"},["b","23a"],["span.small","HEB"],"pitied."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.24a","order":"02.25.022.52339"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/37.1"},"Jer. 37:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"24b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.24b","order":"02.25.022.52341"},["b","24b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/24.6"},"2 Kgs. 24:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/3.16"},"1 Chr. 3:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.25a","order":"02.25.022.52343"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/34.20"},"Jer. 34:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.28a","order":"02.25.022.52345"},["b","28a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/31.12"},"Ps. 31:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.38"},"Jer. 48:38"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/8.8"},"Hosea 8:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"29a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.29a","order":"02.25.022.52347"},["b","29a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.2.1-2"},"D&C 1:2 (1–2)"],"."],["div",{"id":"30a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.30a","order":"02.25.022.52349"},["b","30a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/record-keeping"},"TG Record Keeping"],"."]]}
